RCM’s Konyn to Resign as Asia Chief Executive Officer in March

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-09-06T09:26:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/rcm-s-konyn-to-resign-as-asia-chief-executive-officer-in-march.html
Mark Konyn, the Hong Kong-based
chief executive officer of RCM Asia Pacific Ltd., will resign at
the end of March 2012.  “At this stage of my career, I am looking to take up a new
challenge and to build on my 22 years of experience in Asia,”
Konyn said in an RCM statement dated Sept. 2.  Konyn has been responsible for the company’s investment
business in Hong Kong, Japan and Australia over the past five
years, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marco Lui in Hong Kong at 
 mlui11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  